#Challenge01
'''
Write a Powershell script to 
1. store you name, age and city in variables
2. Prints a message in the format 
    Hello, my name is <name>. I am <age> years old and live in <city>
'''
 
$name="Hrushikesh"
$city= "Hanamkonda"
$age= 23
 
#Single quotes--->no variable expansion
'Hello, my name is $($name). I am $($age) years old and live in $($city).' 
"Hello, my name is $($name). I am $($age) years old and live in $($city)." #double quotes expand the variables